msgid "Keep in mind that Privacy Badger is [not just a tracker blocker](#How-is-Privacy-Badger-different-from-Disconnect%2c-Adblock-Plus%2c-Ghostery%2c-and-other-blocking-extensions).\n"
msgstr "Recuerde que Privacy Badger [no es solamente un bloqueador de rastreadores](#How-is-Privacy-Badger-different-from-Disconnect%2c-Adblock-Plus%2c-Ghostery%2c-and-other-blocking-extensions).\n"

